---
import AnimatedSection from "./AnimatedSection";
import CountUp from "./CountUp";
---

<section id="formacao" class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    <AnimatedSection client:visible>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand">
          Hospital Geral de Fortaleza · HGF/SESA
        </p>
        <h2
          class="mt-3 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-3xl"
        >
          Formação que se traduz em experiência e segurança
        </h2>
      </div>
    </AnimatedSection>

    <AnimatedSection client:visible delay={0.15}>
      <div
        class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:gap-0"
      >
        <div class="flex-1 text-center">
          <p
            class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-6xl"
          >
            <CountUp client:visible to={3} duration={1.5} />
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">
            anos de residência médica
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="hidden h-16 w-px bg-border sm:block" aria-hidden="true">
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 text-center">
          <p
            class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-6xl"
          >
            <CountUp client:visible to={12000} duration={2} />
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">
            atendimentos realizados
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="hidden h-16 w-px bg-border sm:block" aria-hidden="true">
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 text-center">
          <p
            class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-6xl"
          >
            <CountUp client:visible to={1000} duration={2} suffix="+" />
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">
            cirurgias e procedimentos
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </AnimatedSection>

    <AnimatedSection client:visible delay={0.25}>
      <div class="mt-8 py-1 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <span
          class="rounded-full border border-brand/20 bg-brand/5 px-3.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand"
        >
          Cirurgia de catarata
        </span>
        <span
          class="rounded-full border border-brand/20 bg-brand/5 px-3.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand"
        >
          Doenças da retina
        </span>
        <span
          class="rounded-full border border-brand/20 bg-brand/5 px-3.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand"
        >
          Laser ocular
        </span>
        <span
          class="rounded-full border border-brand/20 bg-brand/5 px-3.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand"
        >
          Cirurgias oculares
        </span>
      </div>
    </AnimatedSection>

    <AnimatedSection client:visible delay={0.3}>
      <p
        class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-center text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground"
      >
        Três anos de residência médica em um dos maiores e mais tradicionais
        hospitais públicos do Ceará, com vivência diária em centro cirúrgico,
        ambulatório e emergência — da cirurgia de catarata ao tratamento de
        doenças complexas da retina. Formação que prioriza o rigor técnico, a
        segurança do paciente e a atualização constante.
      </p>
    </AnimatedSection>
  </div>
</section>
